snippet.title: World Titans War | Official Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
WTW is a tactical survival video game inspired by World War II.
Starting as a civilian you will be forced to seek resources to survive. 
Action is divided into two periods: civil time and wartime.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1691480/World_Titans_War/
Web: http://worldtitanswar.com
Discord : https://discord.me/wtw
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/user/WorldTitansWar
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/worldtitanswar_official/
